---
globs: ".overkill/verification/**"
description: "OverkillOS gate enforcement during plans"
---

Do not advance phases without passing defined gates. Do not regress properties that already passed; fix or explicitly re-scope with recorded rationale and evidence.

Plans and execution must respect the artifact contract: required outputs exist, are verifiable, and match the gate checklist. Prefer measurable evidence (tests, logs, diffs) over claims.

When editing verification specs or checklists, keep gate criteria explicit and tied to reproducible verification steps.
